\begin_inset Formula $\overline{A_{\mathrm{covered}}}$
\end_inset

.
 If Equation (
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:06-Coverage_constraint"

\end_inset

) does not hold, the 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

special
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

